---

<Layout
  title="Ventures — Mediainc"
  description="25 years of founding, developing and exiting companies across media, content and culture-adjacent industries — Cimientos, Folio, La Tempestad, Vocero, Trama and more."
>
  <Carousel
    images={mainBannerImages}
    alt="Empresas Mediáticas"
    height="h-[310px]"
    fit="cover"
    interval={4500}
    mobileAspect="29/10"
  />

  <section class="py-8 flex flex-col gap-6 font-medium font-['EB_Garamond'] text-center">
    <h1 class="sr-only">Ventures</h1>
    <p class="text-[22px] md:text-[30px] leading-[1.2] font-medium">
      Over the past 25 years, Media Inc has participated in founding,
      developing, and exiting companies across media, content, and
      culture-adjacent industries.

      These are not archived history. They represent a continuous process of
      building: understanding what creates value in a specific context, and
      knowing when to transform, sell, or close.

      This track record informs everything Media Inc builds today.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 flex flex-col gap-10">
    {empresas.map((e) => (
      <article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-center md:items-start">
        <div class="w-[75%] md:w-4/5 mx-auto md:mx-0">
          <Carousel
            images={e.imagenes}
            alt={e.titulo}
            height="h-[450px]"
            fit="auto"
            interval={4500}
            autoplay={false}
            mobileAspect="8/5"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/5 flex flex-col justify-center items-center md:items-start self-stretch px-2 md:px-0">
          <img
            src={e.logo}
            alt={`${e.titulo} logo`}
            class={e.logoClass}
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <span class="mt-4 text-xs text-white text-center md:text-left font-black uppercase tracking-wider">
            {e.categoria}
          </span>
          <p class="mt-3 text-[#B5B5B5] text-center md:text-left leading-[1.2] text-sm md:text-base">
            {e.descripcion}
          </p>
          <time class="mt-4 text-sm text-white uppercase font-bold tracking-wider">
            {e.fecha}
          </time>
        </div>
      </article>
    ))}
  </section>
</Layout>
